com.sk89q.intake.parametric.binding

Class BindingHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sk89q.intake.parametric.binding.BindingHelper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Binding
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    PrimitiveBindings, StandardBindings

    public class BindingHelper
extends java.lang.Object
implements Binding
    A binding helper that uses the BindingMatch annotation to make writing bindings extremely easy.

    Methods must have the following and only the following parameters:

    • A ArgumentStack
    • A Annotation if there is a classifier set
    • A Annotation[] if there BindingMatch.provideModifiers() is true

    Methods may throw any exception. Exceptions may be converted using a ExceptionConverter registered with the ParametricBuilder.
